section.section:
Of the regional members of the Commission:
One shall be a resident of the Eastern Shore of Maryland;
One shall be a resident of Anne Arundel County, Charles County, Calvert County, or St. Mary's County;
One shall be a resident of Prince George's County;
One shall be a resident of Montgomery County;
One shall be a resident of Baltimore County, Harford County, or Howard County;
One shall be a resident of Baltimore City; and
One shall be a resident of Carroll County, Frederick County, Washington County, Allegany County, or Garrett County.
